WEBVTT

34:25.870 --> 34:27.200 line:80%
we used to buy it

34:27.240 --> 34:29.039 line:80%
at 40 wen a catty
regardless of the season.

34:29.039 --> 34:30.140 line:80%
With today's high meat prices

34:30.140 --> 34:31.740 line:80%
and your excellent quality,

34:31.890 --> 34:34.479 line:80%
I'll give you 50 wen.

34:34.840 --> 34:36.560 line:80%
From now on, you'll make braised meat
in the kitchen.
